    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies the use of H3 and LISP for Geolocation services, utilizing geospatial data to mobility use-cases: fresh HDMaps, Intelligent Driving, Cruise and Parking assists. This is achieved by: - EID addressable geospatial abstraction of road-segments. - EID Interface for detections and Uploads, a geospatial-context. - EID Routing-Sharing hazards, blockages, parking, road-inventory. - Compute-First brokerage of geospatial production &lt;&gt; consumption. - Predefined EID geospatial mcast channels to subscribed clients.</t>
